    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert cold email copywriter. Write a personalized, natural-sounding cold email that sounds like a real professional writing to another professional.\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Do NOT sound like a marketer\n- Do NOT use ALL CAPS, emojis, exclamation marks in subject lines\n- Do NOT use clickbait or hype words (\"revolutionary\", \"game-changing\", \"cutting-edge\")\n- Keep the email body under 120 words (strict limit)\n- Use 5-8 short, clear sentences maximum\n- Return ONLY valid JSON with no markdown, no code blocks, no extra text\n- Format exactly: {\"subject\": \"...\", \"body\": \"...\"}\n\nRECIPIENT:\nName: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.first_name }}\nRole: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.role }}\nCompany: {{ $('Loop Over Items').item.json.company_name }}{{ $json.city ? ' in ' + $json.city : '' }}{{ $json.industry ? ' — ' + $json.industry + ' industry' : '' }}\n\nSENDER:\nName: {{ $json.sender_name }}\nCompany: {{ $json.sender_company }}\nRole: {{ $json.sender_role }}\nWhat you offer: {{ $json.pitch_description }}\n\n{{ $json.clean_website_text && $json.clean_website_text.length > 50 ? 'WEBSITE RESEARCH (use this to personalize — reference 1-2 specific details):\\n' + $json.clean_website_text : 'No website research available. Personalize using the recipient\\'s company name, role, and industry. Mention their company specifically — do not write generically.' }}\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n- Open with a specific observation about their company, role, or industry (not \"I hope this finds you well\")\n- Connect their context to what you offer in 1-2 sentences\n- End with a soft, low-friction CTA (a short question, not a demo request)\n- Sign off as: {{ $json.sender_name }}, {{ $json.sender_role }} at {{ $json.sender_company }}",
